overview.en: ZFT concentrated on the analysis of global mass consumption data and economic model exploration, broke through barriers such as industry, region, currency, etc., and finally integrated global consumption data into the innovative digitalization of consumer assets plus social e-commerce 5.0 technology to improve and upgrade In addition to the decentralized global trade account book of the existing blockchain, the whole process of commodities searching, recording, trade contracts, asset delivery and other trade digitization is realized.
overview.zh: ZFT潜心分析全球海量消费数据及经济模式探索，突破了行业、地域、货币等壁垒，终将全球消费数据融入到创新的消费资产数字化加社交电商5.0技术中，完善并升级了现有区块链去中心化的全球贸易账本，实现商品寻找、记录、贸易合约、资产交割等贸易全过程数字化。
